Show HN: Job board to find sales jobs at a startup
text:
Hi HN,

I designed the site based on what I wanted a couple of years ago when I had been looking for a sales job at a startup.

The search function is largely driven by role (Account Executive, Sale Engineer) and you can further filter by funding round, job experience and remote/hybrid/in-office. Next iteration will include search by salary ranges.

It's very early and any feedback is appreciated!
